{
  "stem": "14463.3",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we lived four people in a place of this size, right, in four [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we had a stove in the middle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was studying at the window, you know, at the window with a lamp from-- you know, from-- with a wick, you know, with a bit of kerosene on the bottom.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's how we were living.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, in there-- so the first thing which I was looking for was education.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So not very far from where we lived was a school, a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it's a-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What do you say in English?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A school of-- no, to learn a trade, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I enrolled in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, I couldn't speak any-- a word of-- I couldn't Russian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could not speak Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I couldn't learn-- in the camp, I didn't learn Russian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I learned Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went to school in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I must say, I was very fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I learned very quickly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because the language is similar, you know, because it's a Slav language.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So from Polish to Russian was not so bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But the writing was bad, you know, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I learned it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I learned it very quickly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I learned it to perfection, actually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that's what I did in Kyzylorda, when I was in the technical college.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then, after being in the technical college for some time-- I don't know in that-- together with the cow there, you know, for six, seven months, or maybe more, I found a place-- actually, I didn't find it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My uncle found it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Opposite him, where he lived in the city, he found a little place-- again, one room, less the cow, right, one room.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we grabbed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
